  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: 'What to expect: 1. Build your lens  2. In device click on "Create Leaderboard" -> a leaderboard with a random name will be created.  3. Then click on "Sumit Score" -> a score of 10 with your name will be added to the leaderboard 4. Repeat step 2 and 3  5. Click on "Load Leaderboard" -> your previous leaderboard will be retrieved   You will see mock up data in Lens Studio, and you will see real entries on device'
